Dependencies 

django
django-pipeline
nodeJS (npm) (??)
Yuglify 
    - npm install -g yuglify 
SCSS/SASS
    - There are a bunch of ways to get SASS, I used Ruby 
    - Whatever you do just change the 'SASS_BINARY' option in the PIPELINE 
      dictionary in MERLIN/settings.py to be the location of the SASS compiler 
      on your system